According to the letter, the roads in Jamner taluka of Jalgaon district are unplanned as rural roads.

The Zila Parishad, Jalgaon has demanded inclusion in the scheme.
Accordingly, the use of these roads as well as the resolution of the Zila Parishad, Jalgaon will be considered.
However, the government was considering upgrading these roads to rural roads.
